{"tid":258362,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【私服】TD Seal 希望戀曲(5) - 端午節活動開跑","createTime":"2017-05-26T05:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T16:11:39.000Z","uid":24163,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5bae29c419208f2de2cb592bc0704cb438302a6b","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:16:43.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲好，我喺湯丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日5月26日，週末3倍經 + 泡點3倍，歡迎各新老手加入<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">今日同大家高度推薦一款<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">【私服】TD Seal 希望戀曲</span></span></strong><a href=\"http://www.tdseal.com/forum.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tdseal.com%2Fforum.php&d=rtu48TbBxRTlrxDLd9TUuDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=909fff11\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tdseal.com/forum.php</a><br />\n<br />\n主城長期多人，唔怕死城無人玩</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Rr2VJHA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRr2VJHA.gif&h=87c74c64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">大量免費時裝，巴絲打同樣啱玩<br />\n</span><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dPGaC4b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdPGaC4b.gif&h=27326b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/OcuEwHA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOcuEwHA.gif&h=d1fc8a31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">仲有情侶系統，啱晒同隻<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><del>左/右手</del></span>仔仔囡囡玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(圖中掛咗7000日，唔同天數唔同Pose)</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/DKxZey4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDKxZey4.gif&h=2ab90217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTG圍爐 歡迎加入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/720KYZR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F720KYZR.jpg&h=a8be38b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEALIrik9AiVCiWCpA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEALIrik9AiVCiWCpA&d=rtu48TbBxRTlrxDLd9TUuDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=52a44152\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEALIrik9AiVCiWCpA</a></div>"},{"pid":"431f9514dcf51b4a47284010ed4e93c6bd9f2a30","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:17:16.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">首先下載主程式<br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.tdseal.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.tdseal.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D3&d=rtu48TbBxRTlrxDLd9TUuDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=d5fff873\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.tdseal.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=3</a><br />\n<br />\n下載完後解壓縮，之後打開登錄器【tdseal.exe】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/06XMx8F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06XMx8F.jpg&h=e1dad648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n登錄器畫面如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pcb2AWX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpcb2AWX.jpg&h=590f1915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後按【註冊帳號】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7X9nYT9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7X9nYT9.jpg&h=b333fab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【財產密碼】請謹記，以後用登錄器買任何道具都喺用【財產密碼】<br />\n<br />\n推薦人如果唔介意可以填【tangyuan】<br />\n正是小弟在下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果填咗推薦人，1 Lv就可以喺RC：27409682<br />\n或者TD SEAL 論壇：<a href=\"http://www.tdseal.com/forum.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tdseal.com%2Fforum.php&d=rtu48TbBxRTlrxDLd9TUuDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=909fff11\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tdseal.com/forum.php</a><br />\n入到GAME開完角色，就可以按圖中嘅在線客服<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5FuR3fu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5FuR3fu.jpg&h=b3951c97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n問GM拎<br />\n1級：雷神之鎚（15天）*1 雷神時裝（15天）*1 女武神*1<br />\n200級：64格物品欄擴充卷（永久）*1 銀行尊榮VIP擴張卡(30天)*2 1000希望點<br />\n<br />\n而我推薦人身份會領取到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2、推廣員獎勵<br />\n推廣人員達5個 可獲得愛騰點3000點<br />\n推廣人員達10個 可獲得愛騰點6000點<br />\n推廣人員達15個 可獲得愛騰點9000點<br />\n推廣人員達20個 可選擇以下特殊獎勵<br />\n①&lsquo;希爾特傳承者&rsquo;稱號【聲望值：237296653】 + 任意時裝365天（馬可系列時裝除外）<br />\n②&lsquo;希爾特傳承者&rsquo;稱號 + 馬可魔法石*12<br />\n<br />\n點數我會諗方法回饋返各位巴絲，唔會獨食難肥的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同時歡迎各巴絲成為推薦人，多人玩多份開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n【4月30日更新：問咗GM，佢話200lv先當達成一個，目前達成兩個】<br />\n<br />\n要設定遊戲畫面大小同視窗化打開【setD3DDevice】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/52647CD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F52647CD.jpg&h=beae078b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n註冊完後，會問是否保存您的註冊信息，如果您記得可以唔洗<br />\n但如果喺自己電腦嘅可以記一記，怕萬一記唔起都可以搵得返<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Q499hn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Q499hn.jpg&h=392e9a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後會重新彈出登錄器，然後輸入剛才註冊嘅帳號密碼<br />\n然後會到依個畫面，按右上嘅(殘體注意)【啟動遊戲】<br />\n應該會有4條線路嘅，因為依家喺台灣，所以用台灣線路<br />\n聽其他巴絲講香港IP用國際會好D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n03C53N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn03C53N.jpg&h=9ced7df0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到遊戲畫面，同樣打返剛才註冊嘅帳號密碼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89312zP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89312zP.jpg&h=9b23913d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成功進入後會有SER選，但其實得一個，選左1就可以了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L2s0U2t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL2s0U2t.jpg&h=5589a84a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到去，按創建，溫馨提示：一個AC可以開5個人物的(後面D鎖唔需要理)<br />\n如果唔小心按到會出現【必須使用角色擴充卷來開啟角色欄位方可創立新的角色】，請無視，因為依家創新角要按中間嘅創建(點舞台前方空白位即可)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hpE4781.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhpE4781.jpg&h=361c0955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n創角色，基本上除咗名同職業之外，其他都可以畀遊戲幣或泡點(51 級掛機就有嘅嘢)，都可以換，包括表情、頭髮顏色、性別<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hr24y7r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHr24y7r.jpg&h=332e9171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n創完角選獅子城即可(又喺得一個選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2A6795D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2A6795D.jpg&h=d8cf51ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正式入到遊戲，可以先打旁邊嘅1 Lv 初級教學稻草人<br />\n(打死後可按鍵盤空白鍵快速執嘢)<br />\n直到掉出1張新手的證明(有多唔緊要，之後可以掉)<br />\n然後找頭上有紅色感嘆號嘅[NPC]希爾特世界的教學特使<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0E89X1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0E89X1.jpg&h=a36caa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對話(可以按鍵盤嘅ENTER快速對話)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/756u831.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F756u831.jpg&h=d06d04fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到依度，請一定要按【1.好 我想要學習新手教學】(按鍵盤數字也可)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9U2n43N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9U2n43N.jpg&h=f4989061&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後重覆對話，直到依度按【1. 在這裡】(按鍵盤數字也可)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EH4q6S8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEH4q6S8.jpg&h=27b328ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼續重覆對話升級，直到出現圖中，即代表新手教學已完成，恭喜!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6p80Bs2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6p80Bs2.jpg&h=1298b035&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後搵[NPC]新手裝備大師，按3【3. 請問現在可以給我禮包了嗎?】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p79Db9W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp79Db9W.jpg&h=22a9d209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n領完後，可按【I】開啟背包<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">謹記除咗教學用帳子同武器之外<br />\n教學用嘅上下鞋都唔好用!!!!!唔好用!!!!!唔好用!!!!!</span></strong></span><br />\n因為你依家著緊嘅高制高防D<br />\n完成圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0N2uzh5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0N2uzh5.jpg&h=059950a9&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"56e0ba986221919a0df2e2232aa54bbdaf48e826","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">搞掂晒之後去開銀行先，圖中紅圈位置<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39SFqnh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39SFqnh.jpg&h=f9d966be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵到之後點佢，之後交易<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R49f379.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR49f379.jpg&h=36ecb0c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會顯示【目前還未開戶、那就幫您開戶喔】<br />\n之後輸入兩次密碼，請謹記密碼，因為唔記得好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞掂之後入一次銀行，睇下入唔入到<br />\n入到嘅畫面，空白一片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放嘢入銀行就喺背包拉入去銀行<br />\n銀行拎嘢出嚟同樣銀行拉入去背包<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M3YTk6y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM3YTk6y.jpg&h=b7c8b0cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後可以熄咗銀行先，最重要一環<br />\n正服需要點數嘅道具有某D私服免費購買<br />\n回到登錄器<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MAD61Qg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMAD61Qg.jpg&h=086a631d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新手需要幾樣道具，依家詳細介紹下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7S8TUgX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7S8TUgX.jpg&h=145ba65d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前期升級好快，所以可以用住商城寵<br />\n鐵甲蟹、[戀曲轟趴]蝙蝠人：依兩隻都喺寵物，可以幫您過前期，到後期都喺建議養鳥蛋系列<br />\n[戀曲轟趴]蝙蝠俠變身戒指：坐騎、喺用[戀曲轟趴]蝙蝠人嘅時候先可以用<br />\n攤販呼叫卷：可隨意開啟攤販，練功唔洗返城買藥水、賣裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n銀行VIP會員卡：可隨意開啟銀行，唔洗返城放裝拎裝<br />\n天神的守護(30天)：自動食藥水(HP、MP)，但只有藥水類，食物類只可以自己食<br />\n寵物便當盒(30天)：自動餵寵，唔洗手動餵<br />\n<br />\n武器類，一開始應該夠錢買15LV嗰把，1萬遊戲幣<br />\n如果之後唔夠錢買，需要錢可以搵我GAME名【牛丸】<br />\n長期在線，歡迎各巴絲搵我拎錢洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(購買遊戲幣類別嘅道具需要放足夠嘅錢入銀行先買到)<br />\n放完後需要重啟登錄器<br />\n(獵人及饕客因為新職業，所以無坦柏特新手武器系列)<br />\n到時如果開咗公會我會盡量打獵人及饕客武放入去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kf8TPV6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkf8TPV6.jpg&h=19f10f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有其他+屬性藥水同時裝就唔一一介紹，因為太多，喺登錄器各買一樣<br />\n之後開返遊戲，按【ALT + I】或點左下瞎拼銀行<br />\n如圖：按O即可<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9B3751.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9B3751.jpg&h=0ebe760d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後將左邊啱啱買嘅道具拉去右邊嘅CASH背包<br />\n(寵物應該會話未夠LV拉唔到出嚟，到夠LV拉出嚟用即可)<br />\n仲會有件套裝、加嘅數值都好高，非常夠用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z6Sdcf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz6Sdcf5.jpg&h=b91698f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲入面有分離式同套裝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2w28VgT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2w28VgT.jpg&h=ef5eab81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n分離式要泡點先買到<br />\n而泡點要遊戲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>等級51</strong></span></span>嘅時候掛機才可取得<br />\n而泡點要遊戲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>等級51</strong></span></span>嘅時候掛機才可取得<br />\n而泡點要遊戲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>等級51</strong></span></span>嘅時候掛機才可取得<br />\n<br />\n套裝用住件原住民即可，當然要靚靚可以任您選免費嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天神的守護(30天)、寵物便當盒(30天)、用咗會喺左上角出現小圖示<br />\n放上去睇可以睇到幾時過期，當然免費可以買多幾個都無問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gb5FAn7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgb5FAn7.jpg&h=0aa70050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到依度差唔多可以去升LV了<br />\n<br />\n新手方面建議玩法師起家<br />\n因為點全智輸出高而且唔會MISS<br />\n非常適合起家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然可以試晒唔同人物啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n配點同技能方面已經唔洗一點一點加同搵技能師學<br />\n全部都完善咗，可以一次過加大量點同自己學技<br />\n<br />\n升級路線方面：<br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.tdseal.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=59\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.tdseal.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D59&d=rtu48TbBxRTlrxDLd9TUuDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=ce622fd0\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.tdseal.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=59</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小提示，隻GAME傳送有兩個方法<br />\n第一：前後期都會用到嘅方法<br />\n喺遊戲對話框輸入【/往XXX】<br />\nXXX喺你想去嘅地圖<br />\n如獅子城 就輪入 /往獅子城(如圖)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/64y0s2D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F64y0s2D.jpg&h=e08dd6c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果傳送唔成功只有兩個可能<br />\n一：唔夠錢<br />\n二：此地圖不能傳送<br />\n<br />\n第二：適合後期用傳送指令去唔到嘅地方<br />\n用攤販呼叫卷，購買一張10萬的【高級回村卷軸】<br />\n(記住唔好就咁用，用咗會飛返去你搵護士記錄咗嘅點度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n然後到獅子城搵[NPC]德瑪西亞傳送、對話後選擇你要去嘅地方<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VD52DyJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVD52DyJ.jpg&h=78c37076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【4月30日更新】</span></span><br />\n去世界唔洗解七彩，可以直接飛過去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7b40yKc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7b40yKc.jpg&h=c2b0e70e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p07CH4D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp07CH4D.jpg&h=c4d4504a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wHX9xn3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwHX9xn3.jpg&h=2ebf7d34&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"6faf13cfd354d9a7d4171e8f43b48e3756764fa9","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:17:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Q&amp;A</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Q：泡點喺乜嚟架?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A：泡點喺你人物等於或超過51級，每上線5分鐘就會有2泡點(有時候有活動會變更)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Q：點樣睇我有幾多泡點?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A：重新登入登錄器，視窗左上角即可查看</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Q：點解我買遊戲幣嘅道具佢話我唔夠錢，但我明明夠架</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A：因為要將遊戲幣放入銀行內，重啟登錄器就會顯示遊戲幣嘅數量，要用放於銀行嘅遊戲幣先可以購買登錄器嘅道具</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Q：打到個【黃金寶箱】，點開架?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A：【黃金寶箱】需要用喺登錄器搜尋【寶石黃金鑰匙】，利用泡點購買</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Q：無錢喎</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">A：入GAME CALL我：牛丸，即可拿取起動基金</span><br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n諗到再打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373a0249f5e9463f80ed038279401a49f099e4f9","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:18:16.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Raidcall 在線貢獻回饋獎勵</span></span><br />\n<br />\n力挺 Raidcall 在線貢獻大回饋獎勵<br />\n（Updata 160111）<br />\n<br />\n理員ID：tdsealol<br />\n管理員名稱：─═❥管理員. ★&gt;〞admin<br />\n群ID：27409682<br />\n<br />\n免費的高級屬性商城時裝等你來!<br />\nPS：在獎勵更新前已領取RC貢獻獎勵的玩家，可以聯繫GM補發獎品內容！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.tdseal.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.tdseal.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D28&d=rtu48TbBxRTlrxDLd9TUuDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=6b4f4196\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.tdseal.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=28</a></div>"},{"pid":"a1e9e9d64378499e2171eae0271eefd2f4d28204","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T06:37:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14b7cf75ea82bf9cbcdb20602eedbbe2785c33e","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88995bd52ce5921f4afc04df856ade515078f11c","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00146e39a6b91931aa767984ab5e924724ca800","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8503ff876121017459eb88ac14a3dbca6d3bf95f","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T18:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4dff20f212e2539a17b3f8d0c506b24e348336","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acedb90a4aecf4ad54b9ddd21e2d6d688af005d6","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c806c8fbb13b60f872f1347333fbdc5897f39e","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T12:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dfa49776457c5cc2609d4795565df7940f9d258","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T21:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87054d566a2296b6b4cff8dded4656fcb04f7c06","tid":258362,"uid":5834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T11:10:02.000Z","msg":"幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22767271109aa682ef7cd6f0cfb843795a299f6","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22ddf9ca9ccfa2765945a96251a1bbaed417d9a","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T10:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062e9736146196d9f0829f1ff8caa941b357dab3","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:08:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c657ac2093332d3ab71d443165b8c9ca37af3e","tid":258362,"uid":5834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T19:52:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9458abc455c270658091056c2d4fa6dc48869f9","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69768cd20a205a201aaf78e455c204a3903a080","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T09:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc18ac40a95f6246fc9eb1126eb97383358c65c","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e59d7e26e35a6f1eae3fbdf232783cb49b7d61","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T15:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3c1a8dae34f9486f556bafc6a204804595a451","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T07:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528ac20eec7090ece51623df51af36ccdd87108a","tid":258362,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}